vestigation%20Discovery%20docuseries%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%3A%20The%20Dark%20Side%20of%20Kids%20TV.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20definitely%20some%20recognizable%20faces%20on%20that%20side%20of%20the%20room.%20And%20my%20side%20was%20me%2C%20my%20mom%2C%20and%20my%20brother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrake-bell-sexual-abuse-nickelodeon-brian-peck-documentary-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeck%2C%20an%20acting%20coach%2C%20was%20charged%20in%202003%20with%20sexually%20abusing%20an%20unnamed%20child%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Until%20now%2C%20Bell%20has%20remained%20anonymous%20as%20the%20child%20in%20the%20criminal%20case.%20In%20May%202004%2C%20Peck%20pleaded%20no%20contest%20to%20two%20of%20the%2011%20charges%3A%20performing%20a%20lewd%20act%20with%2014%20or%2015-year-old%2C%20and%20oral%20copulation%20with%20a%20minor%20under%2016.%20He%20was%20sentenced%20to%2016%20months%20in%20state%20prison%20and%20ordered%20to%20register%20as%20a%20sex%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20in%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%2C%26quot%3B%20premiering%20on%20Sunday%20and%20Monday%2C%20Bell%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20speaking%20publicly%20about%20the%20abuse%20he%20says%20he%20experienced%20when%20he%20was%2015.%20In%202023%2C%20Maxine%20Productions%2C%20one%20of%20the%20docuseries'%20producers%2C%20petitioned%20the%20court%20to%20unseal%20the%20letters%20of%20support%20in%20the%20Peck%20case%3B%20such%20letters%20typically%20offer%20a%20judge%20a%20sympathetic%20perspective%20of%20a%20defendant%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20ahead%20of%20sentencing.%20The%20court%20released%2041%20letters%20that%20Peck's%20friends%20and%20family%20sent%20to%20the%20judge%20on%20Peck's%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProminent%20Hollywood%20insiders%20who%20wrote%20letters%20include%20the%20%26quot%3BX-Men%26quot%3B%20actor%20James%20Marsden%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BGrowing%20Pains%26quot%3B%20star%20Alan%20Thicke%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Meets%20World%26quot%3B%20costars%20Will%20Friedle%20and%20Rider%20Strong%2C%20and%20the%20actor%20and%20comedian%20Taran%20Killam%2C%20who%20would%20later%20become%20a%20cast%20member%20on%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live.%26quot%3B%20Two%20letter%20writers%20%E2%80%94%20Rich%20and%20Beth%20Correll%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0went%20on%20to%20work%20with%20Peck%20on%20the%20Disney%20Channel%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Suite%20Life%20of%20Zack%20%26amp%3B%20Cody%26quot%3B%20after%20Peck%20was%20released%20from%20prison%20and%20registered%20as%20a%20sex%20offender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Bell%20was%20anonymous%20in%20the%20criminal%20case%2C%20some%20letter%20writers%20may%20not%20have%20known%20he%20was%20involved.%20Some%20said%20they%20did%20not%20know%20about%20other%20details%20of%20the%20case.%20The%20%26quot%3BGrowing%20Pains%26quot%3B%20star%20Joanna%20Kerns%20told%20the%20producers%20of%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26quot%3B%20that%20her%20letter%20was%20based%20on%20misinformation.%20%26quot%3BKnowing%20what%20I%20know%20now%2C%20I%20never%20would%20have%20written%26quot%3B%20it%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeck%2C%2063%2C%20built%20a%20career%20in%20Hollywood%20as%20an%20acting%20and%20dialogue%20coach.%20He%20appeared%20in%20minor%20roles%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20'90s%2C%20and%20early%20aughts%2C%20including%20in%20the%20sitcoms%20%26quot%3BGrowing%20Pains%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Meets%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20film%20adaptation%20of%20%26quot%3BHoles%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BX-Men.%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20work%20on%20the%20Nickelodeon%20shows%20%26quot%3BAll%20That%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amanda%20Show.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeck%20developed%20a%20niche%20coaching%20kids.%20In%20the%20early%20'90s%2C%20when%20Peck%20was%20in%20his%2030s%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20a%20young%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20on%20%26quot%3BGrowing%20Pains.%26quot%3B%20A%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20report%20in%202002%20mentioned%20a%20comedy%20boot%20camp%20he%20ran%20with%20Dan%20Schneider%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amanda%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDrake%20%26amp%3B%20Josh%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BiCarly.%26quot%3B%20Several%20people%2C%20including%20Strong%2C%20wrote%20in%20their%20letters%20of%20support%20that%20Peck%20befriended%20them%20when%20they%20were%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%20and%20Friedle%20discussed%20their%20support%20of%20Peck%20on%20a%20February%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BPod%20Meets%20World%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Meets%20World%26quot%3B%20rewatch%20podcast%20they%20cohost%20with%20their%20former%20costar%20Danielle%20Fishel.%20The%20episode%20aired%20after%20the%20producers%20of%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26quot%3B%20reached%20out%20for%20comment.%20(Strong%20and%20Friedle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20the%20producers%20or%20BI.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20call%20him%20the%20Forrest%20Gump%20of%20Hollywood%2C%26quot%3B%20Strong%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20he%20knew%20everybody.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Meets%20World%26quot%3B%20actors%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%20that%20Peck%20acknowledged%20he%20was%20guilty%20of%20something%20involving%20a%20minor.%20But%20Strong%20said%20Peck%20portrayed%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvictim%20of%20jailbait%26quot%3B%20who%20was%20attracted%20to%20a%20young%2C%20%26quot%3Bhot%20guy.%26quot%3B%20Friedle%20said%20that%20when%20he%20attended%20the%20sentencing%20to%20support%20Peck%2C%20Bell's%20mother%20turned%20to%20the%20courtroom%20and%2C%20addressing%20Peck%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BLook%20at%20all%20the%20famous%20people%20you%20brought%20with%20you.%20And%20it%20doesn't%20change%20what%20you%20did%20to%20my%20kid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20sat%20there%20wanting%20to%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedle%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%2C%20what%20the%20hell%20am%20I%20doing%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriedle%20went%20on%20to%20work%20alongside%20Bell%20as%20a%20voice%20actor%20in%20%26quot%3BUltimate%20Spider-Man%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20on%20Disney%20XD%20from%202012%20to%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20release%2C%20Peck%20worked%20on%20three%20episodes%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Suite%20Life%20of%20Zack%20%26amp%3B%20Cody%26quot%3B%20that%20aired%20in%202006%20and%202007%2C%20when%20the%20series'%20stars%2C%20Dylan%20and%20Cole%20Sprouse%2C%20were%20young%20teens.%20Peck%20voiced%20a%20talking%20mirror.%20Rich%20Correll%20is%20listed%20as%20the%20episodes'%20director%2C%20and%20Beth%20Correll%20is%20listed%20as%20the%20first%20assistant%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Corrells%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20producers%20of%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bhad%20no%20input%20or%20involvement%20in%20the%20casting%26quot%3B%20of%20Peck%20on%20the%20Disney%20show.%20They%20said%20that%20when%20they%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20case%2C%20Peck%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20replied%20that%20'the%20problem%20had%20been%20resolved.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20with%20knowledge%20of%20Disney's%20records%20from%20the%20time%20said%20that%20while%20Peck%20performed%20voiceover%20work%2C%20he%20was%20never%20on%20set%20and%20had%20no%20interaction%20with%20the%20cast%20or%20crew%2C%20including%20minors.%20When%20Disney%20learned%20of%20his%20conviction%2C%20the%20person%20said%2C%20Peck%20was%20terminated%20and%20his%20voice%20and%20on-screen%20credits%20were%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26quot%3B%20examines%20how%20iconic%20television%20shows%20of%20the%20'90s%20and%20early%202000s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdan-schneider-nickelodeon-empire-massages-hostile-workplace-allegations-inappropriate-costumes-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailed%20to%20protect%20child%20actors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20Peck%2C%20two%20other%20people%20who%20worked%20at%20Nickelodeon%20were%20charged%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20with%20child%20sex%20abuse.%20In%202003%2C%20Jason%20Handy%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amanda%20Show%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20five%20felony%20counts%20related%20to%20child%20sex%20abuse%3B%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%20six%20years%20in%20prison%20after%20pleading%20no%20contest%20to%20two%20of%20the%20charges.%20In%202005%2C%20a%20Nickelodeon%20Studios%20animator%2C%20Ezell%20Channel%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20charges%20of%20abusing%20a%20child.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%20six%20months%20in%20jail%20for%20a%20battery%20charge%20in%20the%20case%20and%20to%2016%20months%20prison%20time%20for%20a%20felony%20charge%20in%20the%20case%2C%20though%20the%20felony%20conviction%20was%20eventually%20overturned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENickelodeon%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set%26quot%3B%20producers%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Binvestigates%20all%20formal%20complaints%20as%20part%20of%20our%20commitment%20to%20fostering%20a%20safe%20and%20professional%20workplace.%26quot%3B%20The%20network%20added%20that%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Badopted%20numerous%20safeguards%20over%20the%20years%20to%20help%20ensure%20we%20are%20living%20up%20to%20our%20own%20high%20standards%20and%20the%20expectations%20of%20our%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKate%20Taylor%20served%20as%20an%20executive%20producer%20for%20%26quot%3BQuiet%20on%20Set.%26quot%3B%20The%20four-part%20docuseries%20is%20produced%20by%20Maxine%20Productions%2C%20a%20part%20of%20Sony%20Pictures%20Television%20Nonfiction%2C%20in%20association%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20It%20is%20directed%20by%20Mary%20Robertson%20and%20Emma%20Schwartz.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrake-bell-brian-peck-letters-of-supp