%20in%20announcing%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20winner.%C2%A0While%20other%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20put%20out%20lacklustre%20lists%20with%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20the%20seats%20they%20were%20chosen%20for%2C%20Trinamool%20hosted%20a%20gala%20event%20in%20Kolkata's%20Brigade%20ground%20last%20weekend%20to%20introduce%20its%20poll%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20led%20the%20parade%2C%20waving%20to%20the%20crowd%20and%20followed%20by%20the%20party's%2042%20candidates%20for%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bengal.%20Her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20virtually%20the%20No.2%20in%20the%20party%2C%20read%20out%20the%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surprise%20choice%20walked%20right%20behind%20the%20Trinamool%20chief.%20It%20is%20a%20face%20that%20keeps%20Bengali%20women%20in%20and%20outside%20the%20state%20hooked%20to%20the%20TV%20screen%20for%20an%20hour%20daily.%20It%20was%20the%20face%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20born%20Jhumjhum%20Banerjee%2C%20first%20made%20headlines%20back%20in%201994%2C%20when%20she%20was%20crowned%20Miss%20Kolkata.%20She%20later%20went%20on%20to%20star%20in%20films%20across%20several%20languages%2C%20including%20Bengali%2C%20Odia%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20film%20won%20her%20the%20popularity%20that%20a%20TV%20game%20show%20did.%20'Didi%20No.%201'%20was%20launched%20in%202010%20and%20interestingly%2C%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20was%20not%20its%20first%20anchor.%20She%20took%20over%20in%20the%20second%20season%20and%20then%20the%20producers%20tried%20other%20faces%20too%2C%20but%20none%20stuck%20on%20the%20way%20she%20did.%20The%20show%20has%20a%20bit%20of%20everything%20-%20games%2C%20laughter%20and%20emotions.%20Women%20participants%20narrate%20their%20life%20struggles%2C%20share%20their%20happy%20memories%20and%20the%20anchor%20balances%20fun%20and%20sentimentality.%20The%20result%20is%20the%20longest%20running%20Bengali%20game%20show%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20Trinamool%20announced%20its%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20starred%20in%20a%20Didi%20No.%201%20episode.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20few%20people%20had%20thought%20that%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20would%20be%20the%20Trinamool's%20poll%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrity%20candidate%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Hooghly%2C%20a%20suburban%20seat%20near%20Kolkata.%20She%20is%20up%20against%20a%20former%20colleague%20and%20actor-turned-politician%2C%20BJP's%20Locket%20Chatterjee.%20Ms%20Chatterjee%20is%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Hooghly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool's%20choice%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20mood%20of%20this%20election.%C2%A0The%20biggest%20political%20talking%20point%20in%20Bengal%20right%20now%20is%20Sandeshkhali.%20An%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20made%20headlines%20after%20its%20residents%20accused%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%20While%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20its%20local%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20now%20in%20CBI's%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20mob%20attack%20case%2C%20the%20Oppositon%20BJP%20has%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20paint%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20has%20cultivated%20a%20formidable%20support%20base%20among%20women%20through%20schemes%20like%20Kanyashree%2C%20Rupashree%20and%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar.%20That%20is%20now%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20comes%20in.%20Yes%2C%20she%20is%20a%20celebrity%2C%20but%20her%20audience%20cuts%20across%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%20and%20spans%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20propped%20up%20actors%20as%20its%20poll%20picks%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20glitz%20advantage%20comes%20at%20a%20cost.%20Outgoing%20MPs%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%20and%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20pulled%20off%20stunning%20wins%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20but%20the%20party%20had%20to%20tackle%20the%20side-effects%20too.%20Nusrat%20Jahan%2C%20for%20example%2C%20drew%20fire%20for%20posting%20a%20clip%20of%20her%20Valentine's%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20row.%20This%20prompted%20rivals%20to%20target%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20propping%20up%20candidates%20not%20invested%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20strategy%20has%20paid%20off%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee%20so%20far.%20Hence%2C%20the%20former%20celebrity%20picks%20have%20made%20way%20for%20new%20ones.%20But%20with%20Rachana%20Banerjee%2C%20Trinamool%20is%20looking%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20far%20wider%20demographic%20than%20it%20has%20earlier%20done.%20Unlike%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%2C%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20or%20actor%20Dev%20-%20who%20has%20been%20repeated%20as%20a%20candidate%20this%20time%20-%20Rachna%20comes%20on%20TV%20daily.%20Her%20audience%20spans%20across%20economic%20classes%20and%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20sea%20of%20difference%20between%20a%20TV%20studio%20and%20the%20poll%20arena.%20Rachana%20Banerjee%20knows%20there%20are%20no%20retakes%20here.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20she%20has%20said%20the%20shooting%20of%20Didi%20No%201%20may%20face%20disruptions%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20But%20I%20will%20come%20and%20shoot%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Then%20came%20the%20big%20question%3A%20why%20politics%3F%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20need%20power%20and%20a%20platform%20to%20work%20for%20people%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20bigger%20platform%20than%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710331020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1pt3bnno_rachna-banerjee-mamata-banerjee_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20there%20was%20an%20award%20for%20glitz%20quotient%20in%20announcing%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20winner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20troops%20are%20shooting%20at%20balloons%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20beat%20one%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war's%20most%20'dangerous'%20and%20unpredictable%20weapons%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20and%20a%20small%20drone%20holding%20a%20balloon.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0b1f990413ab8e1dbea56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20and%20a%20small%20drone%20holding%20a%20balloon.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESmall%20drones%20have%20emerged%20as%20a%20serious%20problem%20on%20the%20modern%20battlefield%2C%20especially%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military%20is%20training%20service%20members%20how%20to%20engage%20and%20defeat%20this%20dangerous%20threat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20Fort%20Sill%20in%20Oklahoma%2C%20troops%20practice%20shooting%20down%20drones%20by%20firing%20at%20balloons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ordinary%20pink%20balloon%20dangling%20by%20a%20string%20from%20a%20small%20quadcopter%20drone%20shakes%20violently%20in%20the%20wind%20as%20it%20whips%20across%20the%20hills%20of%20southwest%20Oklahoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20National%20Guardsmen%20closely%20track%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20balloon%2C%20which%20is%20unable%20to%20stay%20even%20remotely%20still.%20One%20of%20them%20steadily%20raises%20his%20rifle%20to%20the%20sky.%20A%20few%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20few%20loud%20bangs%20%E2%80%94%20later%2C%20the%20balloon%20is%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20balloon%20wasn't%20dangerous%2C%20but%20it%20represented%20a%20deadly%20and%20terrifying%20threat%20that%20has%20become%20a%20defining%20characteristic%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20one%20that%20the%20US%20military%20is%20now%20training%20to%20fight%20against%3A%20small%20drones%2C%20or%20unmanned%20aircraft%20systems%2C%20that%20can%20be%20packed%20with%20explosives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Guardsmen%20are%20students%20at%20the%20Joint%20C-sUAS%20(Counter-small%20Unmanned%20Aircraft%20System)%20University%2C%20or%20JCU%2C%20a%20new%20US%20Army%20initiative%20based%20at%20Fort%20Sill%2C%20less%20than%20100%20miles%20southwest%20of%20Oklahoma%20City.%20There%2C%20American%20service%20members%20from%20all%20branches%20of%20the%20military%20have%20started%20learning%20how%20to%20identify%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20ultimately%20defeat%20the%20emerging%20drone%20threat%20that%20is%20rapidly%20reshaping%20modern%20battlefields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsmen%20identify%20drones%20with%20their%20instructor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0990a90413ab8e1dbdd25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsmen%20identify%20drones%20with%20their%20instructor.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20everybody's%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20Lt.%20Col.%20Moseph%20Sauda%2C%20the%20JCU%20director%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20during%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Fort%20Sill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20two%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-ukraine-fighting-drone-war-us-military-was-waiting-for-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewar%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20featured%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20all%20shapes%2C%20sizes%2C%20and%20capabilities%20on%20both%20sides.%20Cheap%2C%20commercial%20drones%20in%20particular%20have%20performed%20a%20myriad%20of%20deadly%20tasks.%20Small%20quadcopters%20are%20often%20filmed%20releasing%20explosives%20above%20troops%20and%20armored%20vehicles%20or%20simply%20flying%20into%20them%20and%20detonating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20such%20tactics%20have%20become%20exceedingly%20commonplace%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20they%20are%20not%20unique%20to%20the%20conflict.%20Weaponized%20commercial%20drones%20were%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20used%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fnational-security%2Fuse-of-weaponized-drones-by-isis-spurs-terrorism-fears%2F2017%2F02%2F21%2F9d83d51e-f382-11e6-8d72-263470bf0401_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Islamic%20State%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20mid-2010s.%20Their%20usage%20presented%20a%20new%20headache%20for%20American%20and%20partner%20forces%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20took%20this%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20Sauda%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20prompted%20us%20to%20start%20rethinking%20how%20we%20train%20people%20and%20getting%20some%20weapons%20systems%2C%20and%20just%20systems%20in%20general%2C%20out%20there%20to%20help%20protect%20people%20and%20save%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Operators%20shoot%20at%20a%20balloon%20dangling%20from%20a%20small%20drone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0994dce7f1785b2e8ee24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOperators%20shoot%20at%20a%20balloon%20dangling%20from%20a%20small%20drone.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JCU%2C%20which%20is%20just%20one%20element%20of%20a%20much%20larger%20Pentagon%20response%20to%20combat%20the%20rising%20threat%20of%20drones%2C%20essentially%20emerged%20as%20a%20way%20to%20consolidate%20counter-drone%20training%20for%20service%20members%20across%20the%20US%20armed%20forces%20in%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20October%2C%20hundreds%20of%20US%20troops%20have%20come%20to%20Fort%20Sill%20for%20two-week%20courses%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20understand%2C%20identify%2C%20and%20defeat%20potentially%20hostile%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20here%20is%20to%20standardize%20and%20centralize%20the%20training%2C%20as%20well%20as%20become%20a%20repository%20and%20a%20think%20tank%20for%20this%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20Sauda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20aspect%20of%20the%20training%20involves%20having%20JCU%20pilots%20fly%20small%20drones%20above%20firing%20a%20range%20to%20replicate%20known%20and%20unknown%20threats.%20The%20students%20at%20the%20training%20center%20then%20practice%20engaging%20these%20threats%20using%20the%20Army's%20counter-drone%20equipment%3A%20the%20Drone%20Buster%20and%20the%20Smart%20Shooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Drone%20Buster%20is%20an%20electronic%20warfare%20system.%20A%20user%20can%20point%20it%20at%20the%20drone%2C%20and%20it%20cuts%20the%20signal%20between%20the%20system%20and%20its%20operator.%20A%20second%20service%20member%20standing%20nearby%20can%20then%20use%20a%20Smart%20Shooter%20system%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rifle%20outfitted%20with%20a%20special%20optic%20that%20tracks%20the%20drone%2C%20calculates%20its%20trajectory%2C%20and%20informs%20the%20user%20when%20they%20have%20a%20good%20chance%20of%20hitting%20it%20with%20a%20conventional%20bullet%20%E2%80%94%20to%20neutralize%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20holds%20up%20a%20Drone%20Buster.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f099fdce7f1785b2e8ef02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20holds%20up%20a%20Drone%20Buster.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Smart%20Shooter%20system%20is%20the%20kinetic%20follow%20to%20the%20electronic%20warfare%20component.%20It's%20hard%20enough%20to%20shoot%20a%20drone%20that's%20still%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bnear%20impossible%26quot%3B%20to%20shoot%20one%20that's%20moving%2C%20Jacob%20Cameron%2C%20who%20manages%20the%20JCU's%20aircraft%20and%20pilots%20as%20its%20%26quot%3Bair%20boss%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Smart%20Shooter%20is%20a%20much-needed%20asset%20that%20even%20a%20great%20marksman%20would%20likely%20find%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Drone%20Buster%20and%20Smart%20Shooter%20don't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20be%20used%20together%2C%20but%20they%20work%20best%20if%20they%20are%2C%20Cameron%20said.%20The%20JCU%20also%20employs%20other%20electronic-based%20systems%2C%20like%20early-warning%20radars%2C%20in%20its%20training%20process.%20Detecting%20the%20initial%20threat%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%20of%20the%20counter-drone%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20Drone%20Buster%20and%20Smart%20Shooter%20in%20their%20hands%2C%20two%20National%20Guardsmen%20practiced%20one-on-one%20engagements%20against%20single%20drones%20out%20on%20the%20range%2C%20which%20BI%20observed%20firsthand.%20But%20instead%20of%20shooting%20down%20commercial%20drones%2C%20throwing%20away%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20or%20more%20on%20each%20target%2C%20troops%20went%20up%20against%20simple%20balloons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20cost-saving%20method%2C%20but%20it%20also%20adds%20some%20rigor%20to%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20takes%20aim%20with%20a%20Smart%20Shooter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f09a756080194819ff1dbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Wisconsin%20National%20Guardsman%20takes%20aim%20with%20a%20Smart%20Shooter.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20hit%20a%20balloon%20in%20the%20wind%20in%20Oklahoma%2C%20you%20can%20probably%20hit%20a%20drone%2C%26quot%3B%20Cameron%20said.%20The%20Guardsmen%20agreed%2C%20telling%20BI%20the%20balloons%20provide%20an%20ideal%20training%20target%20because%20of%20the%20erratic%20movement%20in%20the%20wind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20balloons%20won't%20last%20forever%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20JCU%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20start%20incorporating%20its%20own%20cheaply%20manufactured%2C%203D-printed%20drones%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20one-time%20engagements%20within%20the%20next%20six%20to%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20JCU%2C%20operators%20also%20train%20how%20to%20engage%20drone%20swarms%2C%20when%20multiple%20aircraft%20are%20flown%20by%20a%20single%20pilot%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20overwhelm%20defenders%2C%20and%20practice%20defeating%20that%20threat%20through%20electronic%20jamming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20swarm%20exercise%2C%20the%20range%20started%20out%20quiet.%20But%20the%20peaceful%20sound%20of%20the%20Oklahoma%20wind%20quickly%20gave%20way%20to%20the%20ominous%20buzz%20of%20eight%20drones%20closing%20in%20on%20the%20Guardsmen's%20location%20from%20multiple%20directions.%20The%20drones%20were%20unarmed%2C%20but%20they%20were%20meant%20to%20replicate%20a%20terrifying%20aspect%20of%20the%20evolving%20drone%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20drone%20hovers%20above%20the%20firing%20range.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f099a6ce7f1785b2e8ee4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20small%20drone%20hovers%20above%20the%20firing%20range.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Guardsmen%20said%20what%20worries%20them%20most%20about%20the%20drone%20threat%20is%20how%20quickly%20the%20aircraft%20can%20surround%20them%20before%20they%20realize%20what's%20happening.%20The%20widespread%20availability%2C%20low%20cost%2C%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20small%20commercial%20drones%20is%20also%20a%20concern%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20modern%20battlefield%2C%20drones%20have%20made%20it%20such%20that%20soldiers%20must%20assume%20they're%20under%20constant%20surveillance%2C%20which%20ultimately%20forces%20them%20to%20change%20how%20they%20move%20through%20an%20environment%2C%20Sauda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20got%20to%20start%20utilizing%20deception.%20You%20have%20to%20start%20utilizing%20passive%20means%20of%20protection%2C%20hardening%2C%20you%20name%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20technology%2C%20capabilities%2C%20and%20payload%20capacity%20of%20small%20drones%20has%20been%20rapidly%20evolving%20over%20the%20years%2C%20making%20the%20threat%20%26quot%3Bthat%20much%20more%20dangerous%2C%20that%20much%20more%20concerning%2C%26quot%3B%20Cameron%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20great%20for%20the%20hobbyist%2C%20but%20it's%20terrifying%20for%20the%20military%20defender.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops