pite%20rising%20inflation%20over%20the%20years%20and%20putting%20up%20prices%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20range%20from%20wanting%20to%20give%20the%20customer%20a%20positive%20experience%20on%20their%20way%20out%20of%20the%20store%20to%20being%20a%20tactic%20to%20lure%20shoppers%20into%20the%20food%20court%20to%20then%20buy%20other%20pricer%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20David%20Fuller%2C%20assistant%20vice%20president%20of%20publishing%20at%20Costco%2C%20appeared%20to%20settle%20the%20debate%20by%20writing%20in%20the%20store's%20magazine%20that%20its%20steady%20price%20was%20to%20show%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20can%20operate%20on%20a%20fair%20markup%20and%20still%20pay%20all%20of%20its%20bills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHolding%20a%20price%20that%20steady%20for%20that%20long%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20about%20what%20is%20possible%20when%20you%20decide%20to%20operate%20your%20business%20model%20on%20a%20'cost%20plus'%20basis%20instead%20of%20a%20'what%20the%20market%20will%20bear'%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECostco%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20BI's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-hot-dog-soda-combo-deal-wont-be-around-forever-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f17ebdce7f1785b2e91319%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-hot-dog-soda-combo-deal-wont-be-around-forever-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Costco's%20departing%20CFO%20once%20said%20it%20would%20keep%20its%20%241.50%20hotdog-and-soda%20deal%20on%20the%20menu%20forever.%20In%20a%20new%20interview%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20question%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mary%20Hanbury)%22%2C%22engag