quot%3BBefore%20every%20election%2C%20he%20creates%20a%20problem.%20I%20don't%20like%20greedy%20people%20and%20don't%20believe%20in%20dynasty%20politics%2C%20so%20that%20I%20will%20give%20him%20a%20ticket%20in%20elections.%20I%20have%20decided%20to%20disown%20him%20and%20cut%20off%20all%20relationship%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20irascible%20Trinamool%20boss%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20earlier%20Babun%20Banerjee%20criticised%20the%20Trinamool%20for%20its%20selection%20of%20Prasun%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20is%20the%20sitting%20Howrah%20MP.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20selection%20of%20the%20candidate...%20(He)%20is%20not%20the%20right%20choice.%20Many%20capable%20candidates%20who%20were%20overlooked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20never%20forget%20the%20insult%20Prasun%20hurled%20at%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared%2C%20also%20offering%20himself%20as%20a%20candidate.%20And%2C%20in%20a%20sharp%20jab%2C%20he%20suggested%20he%20might%20even%20contest%20the%20seat%20as%20an%20independent%20option%20for%20the%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(as%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20sometimes%20called)%20would%20not%20agree%20with%20me.%20But%2C%20if%20needed%2C%20I%20will%20contest%20as%20independent%20from%20Howrah%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrasun%20Banerjee%20is%20a%20three-time%20winner%20of%20the%20prestigious%20Howrah%20seat%2C%20which%20has%20been%20held%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20since%20Ambica%20Banerjee%20won%20it%20off%20the%20Communist%20Party%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20move%20also%20comes%20amid%20speculation%20her%20brother%20could%20make%20a%20shock%20switch%20to%20rivals%20BJP%2C%20for%20whom%20the%20capture%20of%20an%20archrival's%20family%20member%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20brother%20has%20insisted%20talk%20of%20such%20a%20jump%20is%20unfounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20Mamata%3Cem%3Edi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20there%2C%20I%20will%20never%20quit%20and%20neither%20will%20I%20join%20any%20other%20party.%20Yes%2C%20as%20I%20am%20connected%20to%20sports%20I%20know%20many%20BJP%20leaders...%20who%20are%20also%20connected%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20re-assurances%2C%20though%2C%20were%20not%20sought%20by%20Ms%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20can%20do%20whatever%20he%20wants%20to.%20The%20party%20stands%20by%20its%20official%20candidate%20-%20Prasun%20Banerjee.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20time%20Ms%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20brother%20have%20squabbled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20she%20reprimanded%20him%20publicly%20for%20%26quot%3Broaming%20around%20with%20a%20Covid%20case%20at%20home%26quot%3B.%20Bengal%20was%20then%20reporting%20a%20surge%20in%20infections%20with%20over%2014%2C000%20cases%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-disowns-brother-babun-banerjee-but-this-isnt-their-1st-public-spat-5230509%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20Disowns%20Brother%20Babun%2C%20But%20This%20Isn't%201st%20Public%20Spat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20this%20week%20announced%20candidates%20for%20all%2042%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20Mahua%20Moitra%20-%20controversially%20suspended%20from%20Parliament%20-%20re-nominated%20from%20Krishnanagar%20and%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20nephew%2C%20Abhishek%2C%20to%20defend%20his%20Diamond%20Harbour%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20party%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20had%20hoped%20to%20broker%20a%20three-way%20seat-share%20deal%2C%20including%20with%20Left%20parties%20that%20Ms%20Banerjee%20sees%20as%20a%20