clusive%3A%20Sachin%20Pilot%20On%20Poll%20Pass%20To%20Junior%20Gehlot%2C%20His%20Election%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20in%20the%20Congress%20choosing%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20son%20Vaibhav%20and%20Kamal%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20contests%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20told%20NDTV%2C%20while%20stressing%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20gives%20poll%20chances%20to%20many%20leaders%20whose%20fathers%20are%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20chat%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20election%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20the%20Congress%20has%20chosen%20its%20candidates%20after%20surveys%20and%20factoring%20in%20all%20equations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20released%20names%20of%20its%20candidates%20for%2082%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20so%20far.%20The%20party%20has%20named%20its%20choices%20for%2010%20out%20of%20Rajasthan's%2025%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20second%20list%20was%20out%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20on%20whether%20Mr%20Pilot%20will%20be%20fielded%20from%20the%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur%20seat.%20He%20currently%20represents%20the%20Tonk%20Assembly%20constituency.%20The%20Congress%2C%20however%2C%20chose%20former%20IPS%20officer%20Harish%20Chandra%20Meena%20for%20Tonk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20will%20be%20contesting%20the%20general%20election%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20I%20want%20to%20fight%20or%20not.%20I%20will%20do%20what%20the%20party%20tells%20me.%20I%20have%20contested%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20government.%20I%20am%20now%20in%20charge%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%20We%20have%2011%20seats%20there.%20That%20is%20my%20responsibility%2C%20as%20is%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20did%20not%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20Rajasthan%20in%20the%202014%20and%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%20Some%20reports%20have%20claimed%20that%20looking%20at%20the%20dismal%20poll%20record%20of%20the%20party%2C%20many%20senior%20leaders%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20contest%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20party's%20poor%20record%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20two%20elections%2C%20we%20did%20not%20open%20our%20account.%20This%20time%2C%20we%20will%20win%20with%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20of%20candidates%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20a%20joint%20exercise.%20%26quot%3BAll%20candidates%20are%20our%20candidates.%20If%20Nakul%20Nath%20and%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20get%20tickets%2C%20what%20is%20wrong%20with%20it%3F%20Vaibhav%20did%20not%20win%20the%20last%20time%2C%20so%20the%20party%20has%20given%20him%20a%20second%20chance.%20There%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20as%20long%20as%20we%20win.%20Many%20people%20in%20the%20BJP%20get%20tickets%20and%20their%20father%20and%20grandfathers%20are%20politicians.%20No%20one%20talks%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20are%20significant%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20intense%20rivalry%20between%20Mr%20Pilot%20and%20the%20senior%20Gehlot%20to%20control%20the%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20infighting%20had%20almost%20toppled%20the%20Congress-led%20government%20in%202020%20when%20Mr%20Pilot%20led%20a%20mutiny%20with%20a%20considerable%20chunk%20of%20MLAs.%20While%20the%20Congress%20had%20then%20managed%20to%20contain%20the%20damage%2C%20the%20tussle%20within%20the%20state%20unit%20remained.%20The%20rivalry%20between%20Mr%20Gehlot%20and%20Mr%20Pilot%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Congress's%20rout%20in%20the%20state%20polls%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20elections%20approaching%2C%20the%20party%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20put%20a%20united%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaibhav%20Gehlot%20had%20contested%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20Jodhpur%20but%20lost%20to%20BJP%20heavyweight%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%20Following%20the%20election%2C%20the%20gloves%20were%20off%20and%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20had%20held%20Mr%20Pilot%2C%20then%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%2C%20responsible%20for%20his%20son's%20loss.%20In%20an%20interview%20in%202022%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20fielded%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20in%20the%202019%20election%20on%20his%20insistence.%20He%20had%20also%20backed%20the%20junior%20Gehlot%20after%20the%20central%20agencies%20raided%20his%20premises%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fipe4d2o_sachin-pilot_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-ashok-gehlot-lok-sabha-polls-nothing-wrong-sachin-pilot-after-ashok-gehlots-son-gets-poll-chance-5230344%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20in%20the%20Congress%20choosing%20Ashok%20Gehlot's%20son%20Vaibhav%20and%20Kamal%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20contests%2C%20senior%20party%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20told%20NDTV%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-ashok-gehlot-lok-sabha-polls-nothing-wrong-sachin-pilot-after-ashok-gehlots-son-gets-poll-chance-5230344%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-ashok-gehlot-lok-sabha-polls-nothing-wrong-sachin-pilot-after-ashok-gehlots-son-gets-poll-chance-5230344%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsachin-pilot-ashok-gehlot-lok-sabha-polls-nothing-wrong-sachin-pilot-after-ashok-gehlots-son-gets-poll-chance-5230344%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20have%20decided%20to%20disown%20him'%3A%20Mamata%20slams%20brother%20after%20he%20objects%20to%20Howrah%20candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108463532%2Cimgsize-32900.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fi-have-decided-to-disown-him-mamata-slams-brother-babun-after-he-objects-to-trinamools-howrah-candidate%2Farticleshow%2F108463368.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lawyers%E2%80%99%20Body%20Urges%20CJI%20to%20Take%20Action%20Against%20UP%20Judge%20for%20Making%20Communal%20Remarks%20in%20Judgment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13145914%2FFYj9tb5UIAEsBYD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20pan-India%20organisation%20of%20lawyers%20has%20written%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20demanding%20action%20against%20a%20judge%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20who%2C%20while%20issuing%20an%20order%20in%20the%20trial%20of%20a%202010%20riots%20case%2C%20hailed%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20and%20blamed%20Muslims%20for%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20the%20All-India%20Lawyers%E2%80%99%20Association%20for%20Justice%20(AILAJ)%20also%20requested%20that%20the%20unnecessary%20observations%20made%20by%20judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20in%20his%20March%205%20order%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20record.%20AILAJ%20said%20judge%20Diwakar%E2%80%99s%20statements%20and%20conclusions%20in%20the%20order%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversial%2C%20prejudicial%2C%20bigoted%20and%20unconstitutional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20body%20also%20accused%20judge%20Diwakar%20of%20displaying%20a%20%E2%80%9Csympathy%20for%20a%20majoritarian%20viewpoint%E2%80%9D%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20duty%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitution%20and%20its%20fundamental%20values%2C%20and%20blatantly%20displaying%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdisregard%20for%20constitutional%20morality.%E2%80%9D%20This%20could%20not%20go%20unpunished%2C%20said%20the%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%2C%20additional%20district%20judge-fast%20track%20court%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20on%20March%205%20%E2%80%93%20while%20invoking%20serious%20criminal%20charges%2C%20including%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20against%20prominent%20Muslim%20cleric-politician%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%2C%20for%20communal%20violence%20in%20Bareilly%20in%202010%20%E2%80%93%20hailed%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20occupying%20the%20seat%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20order%2C%C2%A0judge%20Diwakar%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20served%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20passed%20controversial%20orders%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter%2C%C2%A0made%C2%A0a%20string%20of%20seemingly%20controversial%20and%20debatable%20observations.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20lavish%20Adityanath%20with%20praise%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20but%20he%20also%20blamed%20the%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20(Muslims)%20by%20political%20parties%20for%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20and%20reflected%20on%20his%20own%20record%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20legal%20battle%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20and%20his%20family%20were%20living%20under%20fear%20after%20receiving%20threats%20from%20Muslim%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%20described%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20modern-day%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20concept%20of%20theocratic%20ruler%20propounded%20by%20ancient%20Greek%20philosopher%20Plato%20in%20his%20work%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20further%20remarked%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20reason%20for%20riots%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20parties%20here%20are%20engaged%20in%20appeasement%20of%20a%20particular%20religion.%E2%80%9D%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20the%20morale%20of%20prominent%20people%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20increases%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20believe%20that%20even%20if%20they%20cause%20riots%2C%20no%20harm%20will%20fall%20upon%20them%20due%20to%20protection%20provided%20by%20power%2C%20said%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AILAJ%20said%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20judge%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Ceffect%20of%20perpetuating%20misplaced%20stereotypes%20and%20bigoted%20impressions%20about%20the%20Muslim%20community.%E2%80%9D%20In%20making%20these%20statements%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20reveal%20manifest%20bias%20and%20prejudice%20against%20the%20Muslim%C2%A0%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%C2%A0failed%20the%20basic%20standards%20of%20judicial%20conduct%20thereby%20shaking%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%C2%A0confidence%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20said%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20order%20has%20tipped%20the%20scales%20of%20justice%2C%20breached%20the%20avowed%20principle%20of%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20is%20damaging%20to%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20judiciary.%20It%20represents%20an%20abject%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Judge%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20standards%20and%20norms%20bearing%20on%20judicial%20officers%20i.e.%20to%20maintain%20independence%2C%20impartiality%20and%20propriety%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20AILAJ%20in%20its%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0AILAJ%20clarified%20that%20its%20objection%20was%20not%20in%20regard%20to%20the%20judicial%20order%2C%20but%20solely%20limited%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexcessive%20and%20unnecessary%20obiter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%202010%20Bareilly%20riots%20case%2C%20judge%20Diwakar%20added%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2011.%20Khan%20is%20a%20prominent%20cleric%20of%20the%20Barelvi%20sect%20and%20president%20of%20the%20political%20party%20Ittehad-e-Millat%20Council.%20The%20judge%20dubbed%20Khan%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20mastermind%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20on%20March%202%2C%202010%2C%20after%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20route%20of%20a%20Muslim%20religious%20procession.%20Several%20persons%20were%20injured%20and%20properties%20damaged%20in%20the%20incident.%20A%20curfew%20had%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20city%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAILAJ%20also%20expressed%20objection%20to%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20direction%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20order%20be%20sent%20to%20Adityanath%20so%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20could%20take%20action%20against%20those%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20officials%20who%20allegedly%20assisted%20the%20accused%20Muslim%20cleric%20Khan%20and%20did%20not%20act%20as%20per%20law%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20then%20government.%20UP%20was%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20led%20by%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20judicial%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20courts%20has%20an%20inescapable%20significance%2C%20not%20merely%20for%C2%A0the%20determination%20of%20inter%20se%20rights%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20impact%20it%20has%20on%20society%20and%20its%20views%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevious%20judgements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20serving%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202022%2C%20Diwakar%20had%20passed%20controversial%20directions%20regarding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%20Diwakar%2C%20as%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%2C%20had%20ordered%20the%20sealing%20of%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Mosque%20after%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20claimed%20that%20a%20stone%20found%20in%20the%20ablution%20tank%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eshivling%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20had%20given%20his%20nod%20to%20the%20videography%20inside%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20advocate%20commissioner%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20five%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20demanding%20daily%20access%20to%20prayer%20to%20an%20alleged%20Hindu%20side.%20%E2%80%98Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20was%20located%20outside%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAILAJ%20requested%20the%20CJI%20to%20take%20necessary%20action%20against%20judge%20Diwakar%2C%20including%20skill%20development%20at%20the%20judicial%20academy.%20The%20lawyers%20body%20said%20that%20the%20judge%20met%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Curt%20had%20called%20%E2%80%9Cparameters%20for%20upgradation%20of%20skills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20order%2C%20judge%20Diwakar%20had%20observed%20that%20if%20a%20religious%20person%20occupies%20a%20seat%20of%20power%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20good%20results.%20%E2%80%9CJustice%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20a%20king%2C%E2%80%9Dsaid%20Diwakar%2C%20quickly%20adding%20that%20even%20though%2C%20in%20the%20present%20times%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20in%20the%20legal%20sense%2C%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Plato%20it%20was%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20head%20of%20power%20should%20be%20a%20religious%20person%2C%20because%20the%20life%20of%20a%20religious%20person%20is%20not%20one%20of%20enjoyment%20but%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20dedication.%20An%20example%20of%20this%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Epeethadeshwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20great%20Siddhapeeth%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20%3Cem%3Emahant%20baba%20shri%3C%2Fem%3E%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20ji%2C%20who%20is%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20has%20proven%20the%20above%20concept%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20judge%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20however%2C%20if%20any%20religious%20person%20acts%20contrary%20to%20the%20aforementioned%2C%20such%20as%20provoking%20people%20of%20this%20community%2C%20then%20law%20and%20order%20gets%20disrupted%20and%20riots%20occur%2C%20said%20the%20judge.%20Diwakar%20said%20an%20example%20of%20this%20was%20Maulana%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13145914%2FFYj9tb5UIAEsBYD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flawyers-body-urges-cji-to-take-action-against-up-judge-for-making-communal-remarks-in-judgment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20hailed%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20and%20blamed%20Muslims%20for%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20while%20passing%20an%20order%20in%20a%202010%20riot%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flawyers-body-urges-cji-to-take-action-against-up-judge-for-making-communal-remarks-in-judgment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Defamation%20Case%20Against%20Meghan%20Markle%20By%20Half-Sister%20Dismissed%20By%20US%20Judge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20judge%20threw%20out%20a%20defamation%20lawsuit%20filed%20against%20Meghan%20Markle%20by%20her%20half-sister%2C%20Samantha%20Markle.%20Samantha%20claimed%20Meghan's%20comments%20in%20a%20Netflix%20documentary%20and%20an%20interview%20with%20Oprah%20Winfrey%20defamed%20her%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68550942%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%2C%20Charlene%20Edwards%20Honeywell%2C%20ruled%20that%20Meghan's%20statements%20were%20either%20opinions%2C%20mostly%20accurate%20or%20didn't%20damage%20Samantha's%20reputation%20believably.%20Importantly%2C%20the%20case%20was%20dismissed%20permanently%2C%20meaning%20Samantha%20can't%20sue%20again%20over%20the%20same%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20point%20of%20contention%20was%20Samantha's%20claim%20that%20Meghan%20Markle%20said%20she%20only%20changed%20her%20last%20name%20back%20to%20Markle%20after%20Meghan%20started%20dating%20Prince%20Harry.%20However%2C%20the%20judge%20noted%20that%20Samantha%20used%20the%20last%20name%20Rasmussen%20in%202016%20and%20then%20switched%20to%20Markle%20two%20months%20later%2C%20around%20the%20time%20news%20of%20Meghan's%20royal%20connection%20became%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20her%20ruling%2C%20Judge%20Honeywell%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20taken%20notice%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20%5BSamantha%5D%20used%20the%20surname%20Rasmussen%20in%20September%202016%20and%20Markle%20two%20months%20later%2C%20soon%20after%20%5BMeghan's%5D%20royal%20relationship%20was%20first%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20the%20gist%20of%20the%20statement%20-%20that%20%5BSamantha%5D%20switched%20to%20her%20family%20name%20a%20short%20time%20after%20it%20was%20reported%20%5BMeghan%5D%20was%20involved%20with%20Prince%20Harry%20-%20is%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20point%20of%20contention%20was%20Meghan's%20description%20of%20their%20childhood%20bond.%20Meghan%20Markle%20told%20Oprah%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20as%20an%20only%20child%2C%20which%20everyone%20who%20grew%20up%20around%20me%20knows%2C%26quot%3B%20implying%20they%20weren't%20close.%20%C2%A0However%2C%20the%20judge%20sided%20with%20Meghan%2C%20considering%20this%20an%20opinion%20about%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dismissal%20adds%20another%20layer%20to%20the%20ongoing%20legal%20battle.%20%C2%A0This%20was%20actually%20Samantha's%20third%20attempt%20to%20sue%20Meghan%20based%20on%20defamation.%20Previously%2C%20in%202022%2C%20she%20claimed%20Meghan%20spread%20lies%20by%20contributing%20to%20an%20unauthorized%20biography%20and%20by%20discussing%20their%20relationship%20on%20television.%20%C2%A0The%20judge%20dismissed%20that%20case%20too%2C%20finding%20Meghan%20couldn't%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20book's%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fm5a2ksoo_meghan-markle-afp-_625x300_09_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdefamation-case-against-meghan-markle-by-half-sister-dismissed-by-us-judge-5230748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20judge%2C%20Charlene%20Edwards%20Honeywell%2C%20ruled%20that%20Meghan's%20statements%20were%20either%20opinions%2C%20mostly%20accurate%20or%20didn't%20damage%20Samantha's%20reputation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdefamation-case-against-meghan-markle-by-half-sister-dismissed-by-us-judge-5230748%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20Disowns%20Brother%20Babun.%20She%20Had%20Warned%20Him%202%20Years%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20cut%20all%20ties%20with%20her%20younger%20brother%20Babun%20Banerjee%20after%20he%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20party's%20Howrah%20pick%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20siblings%20have%20fought%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20has%20rebuked%20her%20brother%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20for%20violating%20safety%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20told%20off%20her%20brother%20publicly%20for%20%26quot%3Broaming%20around%20with%20a%20Covid%20case%20at%20home%26quot%3B.%20Bengal%20was%20