ed%20to%20disown%20him%20and%20cut%20off%20all%20relations%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20reports%20that%20her%20brother%20might%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20can%20do%20whatever%20he%20wants.%20The%20party%20stands%20by%20its%20official%20candidate%20Prasun%20Banerjee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710324840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fdi0jlbm_babun-banerjee-_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-disowns-brother-babun-banerjee-but-this-isnt-their-1st-public-spat-5230509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20cut%20all%20ties%20with%20her%20younger%20brother%20Babun%20Banerjee%20after%20he%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20party's%20Howrah%20pick.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-disowns-brother-babun-banerjee-but-this-isnt-their-1st-public-spat-5230509%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-disowns-brother-babun-banerjee-but-this-isnt-their-1st-public-spat-5230509%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-disowns-brother-babun-banerjee-but-this-isnt-their-1st-public-spat-5230509%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Third%20Marriage%20extended%20by%2010%20episodes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710324663000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108463296%2Cimgsize-79242.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fthe-third-marriage-levels-up-series-extended-by-10-episodes%2Farticleshow%2F108463306.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%