d%20it%20was%20his%20thinking%20that%20weaker%20sections%20and%20poor%20should%20get%20benefits%20at%20their%20doorsteps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaini%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20the%20'Beti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%20programme%20in%202015%20and%20added%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20took%20it%20as%20a%20pledge%20to%20ensure%20success%20of%20the%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710323040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbpdjkd8_nayab-singh-saini-haryana-chief-minister_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-haryana-chief-minister-clears-floor-test-day-after-bjp-jjp-alliance-ends-5230243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister%20Nayab%20Saini%20cleared%20a%20floor%20test%20aimed%20at%20proving%20that%20BJP%20had%20majority%20status%20in%20the%20assembly%20even%20after%20breaking%20ties%20with%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20JJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-haryana-chief-minister-clears-floor-test-day-after-bjp-jjp-alliance-ends-5230243%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-haryana-chief-minister-clears-floor-test-day-after-bjp-jjp-alliance-ends-5230243%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-haryana-chief-minister-clears-floor-test-day-after-bjp-jjp-alliance-ends-5230243%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Polio-Infected%20Man%2C%20Who%20Spent%2070%20Years%20Inside%20An%20Iron%20Lung%2C%20Dies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaul%20Alexander%2C%20the%20man%20who%20spent%2070%20years%20inside%20an%20iron%20lung%2C%20has%20died%20at%20the%20age%20of%2078.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20live%20inside%20the%20600-pound%20metallic%20structure%20after%20being%20struck%20down%20by%20polio%20at%20the%20age%20of%20six.%20Widely%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BPolio%20Paul%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Alexander%20was%20paralysed%20from%20the%20neck%20down%20since%201952%20due%20to%20the%20disease%2C%20leaving%20him%20unable%20to%20breathe%20by%20himself.%20He%20was%20rushed%20to%20hospital%20in%20Texas%20after%20developing%20symptoms%2C%20and%20woke%20up%20inside%20the%20mechanical%20lung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20death%20was%20announced%20on%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2FIronLungsPaul%5C%22%3EGoFundMe%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012).%20%26quot%3BAfter%20surviving%20polio%20as%20a%20child%2C%20he%20lived%20over%2070%20years%20inside%20of%20an%20iron%20lung.%20In%20this%20time%20Paul%20went%20to%20college%2C%20became%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20a%20published%20author.%20His%20story%20traveled%20wide%20and%20far%2C%20positively%20influencing%20people%20around%20the%20world.%20Paul%20was%20an%20incredible%20role%20model%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20remembered%2C%26quot%3B%20Christopher%20Ulmer%2C%20who%20had%20set%20up%20the%20page%2C%20said%20in%20the%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20message%20from%20his%20brother%20Philip%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20so%20grateful%20to%20everybody%20who%20donated%20to%20my%20brother's%20fundraiser.%20It%20allowed%20him%20to%20live%20his%20last%20few%20years%20stress-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alexander%20faced%20many%20challenges%20since%20he%20was%20born%20in%201946.%20He%20endured%20the%20worst%20polio%20outbreak%20in%20US%20history%20with%20almost%2058%2C000%20cases%20-%20mostly%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20New%20York%20Post%20report%2C%20the%20disease%20severely%20affected%20Mr%20Alexander%2C%20requiring%20him%20to%20use%20a%20machine%20to%20breathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolion%2C%20or%20Poliomyelitis%2C%20is%20a%20disabling%20and%20life-threatening%20disease%20caused%20by%20the%20poliovirus.%20The%20virus%20spreads%20from%20person%20to%20person%20and%20can%20infect%20a%20person's%20spinal%20cord%2C%20causing%20paralysis.%20It%20made%20Mr%20Alexander%20too%20weak%20to%20breathe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underwent%20an%20emergency%20tracheotomy%20and%20was%20placed%20in%20an%20iron%20lung%20to%20help%20his%20body%20combat%20the%20deadly%20disease.%20He%20relied%20on%20the%20neck-to-toe%20machine%20to%20survive%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iron%20lung%20employs%20a%20technique%20called%20%26quot%3Bfrog%20breathing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20uses%20the%20throat%20muscles%20to%20force%20air%20past%20the%20vocal%20cords%2C%20allowing%20the%20patient%20to%20swallow%20oxygen%20one%20mouthful%20at%20a%20time%2C%20pushing%20it%20down%20the%20throat%20and%20into%20the%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710322680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fov63bdd8_paul-alexander-polio-1200_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-who-spent-70-years-inside-an-iron-lung-dies-5230523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paul%20Alexander%20faced%20many%20challenges%20since%20he%20was%20born%20in%201946.%20He%20endured%20the%20worst%20polio%20outbreak%20in%20US%20history%20with%20almost%2058%2C000%20cases%20-%20mostly%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-who-spent-70-years-inside-an-iron-lung-dies-5230523%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-who-spent-70-years-inside-an-iron-lung-dies-5230523%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-infected-man-who-spent-70-years-inside-an-iron-lung-dies-5230523%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Ukraine%20controversy%2C%20Pope%20again%20condemns%20'madness%20of%20war'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710322150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F