sid-108458736%2Cimgsize-24798.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fin-ups-lucknow-mallwoman-caught-clinging-to-moving-cars-doorviral-video-latest%2Farticleshow%2F108458764.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20clinging%20to%20a%20car%20door%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20sparked%20concerns%20about%20whether%20it%20was%20a%20planned%20stunt%20or%20a%20safety%20issue.%20The%20incident's%20location%20near%20Phoenix%20Palassio%20Mall%20raised%20further%20questions.%20The%20response%20of%20Lucknow%20Police%20ensured%20intervention%20and%20appropriate%20measures%20through%20an%20inquiry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fin-ups-lucknow-mallwoman-caught-clinging-to-moving-cars-doorviral-video-latest%2Farticleshow%2F108458764.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Era%20of%20the%20Silenced%20Academic%20Must%20End%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21130942%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-21-at-1.06.53-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcademic%20freedom%20has%20become%20a%20central%20issue%20of%20concern%20in%20India.%20Many%20have%20blamed%20the%20illiberal%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20quality%20of%20individual%20institutions%20in%20question%20for%20the%20decline%20in%20academic%20freedom.%20While%20all%20of%20these%20are%20important%20factors%2C%20the%20question%20of%20academic%20freedom%20is%20complex%20and%20cannot%20be%20easily%20answered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20many%20have%2C%20nevertheless%2C%20noticed%20the%20V-Dem%20Academic%20Freedom%20Index%20(AFI)%20published%20in%202023%20in%20which%20India%20is%20ranked%20in%20the%20bottom%2020-30%25%20category%20below%20countries%20such%20as%20Libya%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Ethiopia%2C%20Chad%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20Palestine.%20In%20the%202024%20report%20published%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20India%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic-freedom-index.net%2Fresearch%2F%5C%22%3Efurther%20pushed%20to%20the%2010-20%20%25%20category%3C%2Fa%3E%20placed%20between%20Rwanda%20and%20South%20Sudan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20situation%20is%20so%20dire%20that%20even%20the%20reputed%20institutions%20do%20not%20fully%20comprehend%2C%20practice%2C%20and%20respect%20academic%20freedom%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20Faculty%20members%20can%20get%20fired%20for%20reasons%20as%20silly%20as%20publishing%20a%20critical%20piece%2C%20supporting%20a%20cause%2C%20clothing%20in%20certain%20ways%20and%20even%20smoking!%20So%2C%20what%20explains%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMedieval%20India%20and%20Europe%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20the%20West%20historically%20had%20two%20distinct%20traditions%20of%20education.%20Colonial%20experience%2C%20however%2C%20changed%20the%20way%20India%20learned%20and%20taught.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20a%20number%20of%20great%20universities%2C%20many%20of%20them%20centuries%20older%20than%20any%20in%20the%20West.%20Some%20of%20them%2C%20such%20as%20Nalanda%20and%20Taxila%2C%20attracted%20scholars%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20India%20had%20its%20share%20of%20brilliant%20rational%20and%20materialistic%20thinkers%2C%20mathematicians%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20geographers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20this%20glorious%20era%2C%20the%20Indian%20system%20of%20higher%20education%20began%20to%20decline%20into%20mindless%20ritual%20and%20repetition.%20It%20became%20regimented%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20caste%20and%20a%20strict%20code%20of%20conduct%20came%20into%20place%20that%20opposed%20the%20spread%20of%20enlightenment.%20The%20notorious%20edicts%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EManusmriti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20other%20ancient%20texts%20embody%20this%20decay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fugc-directs-universities-to-screen-modis-speech-organise-event-with-viksit-bharat-posters%5C%22%3EUGC%20Directs%20Universities%20to%20Screen%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Speech%2C%20Organise%20Event%20With%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20Posters%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20education%20merely%20enabled%20a%20person%20to%20become%20the%20guarantor%20and%20maintainer%20of%20tradition%20and%20not%20its%20challenger%2C%20disruptor%2C%20or%20reformer.%20It%20emphasised%20rote%20learning%20and%20ritual%20while%20discouraging%20creativity.%20It%20routinely%20punished%20students%20for%20questioning%20authority%20and%20ritual.%20Critical%20thought%20was%20suppressed%20as%20feudal%20allegiance%20was%20constantly%20demanded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20followed%2C%20with%20steadfast%20astuteness%2C%20the%20ancient%20Greek%20tradition%20of%20education.%20It%20was%20largely%20secular%20and%20focused%20on%20the%20individual%20rather%20than%20communities.%20Massive%20events%20such%20as%20the%20French%20Revolution%20made%20sure%20that%20education%20shaped%20the%20public%20by%20enhancing%20enlightenment%20and%20reason.%20While%20this%20was%20in%20no%20way%20perfect%2C%20the%20freedom%20to%20think%20and%20publish%20was%20cherished%20and%20promoted.%20The%20separation%20of%20church%20and%20state%20led%20to%20more%20secular%20and%20rational%20thought.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModern%20higher%20education%20in%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20persistent%20nature%20of%20the%20ancient%20Indian%20tradition%20insisted%20that%20children%20take%20up%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20professions.%20Even%20those%20educated%20in%20the%20West%20came%20back%20to%20settle%20in%20India%2C%20keeping%20the%20ancient%20rules%20of%20privilege%20intact.%20Education%20was%20either%20a%20means%20to%20achieve%20%E2%80%98a%20dream%20job%E2%80%99%20or%20a%20choice%20of%20the%20parents.%20It%20was%20rarely%20a%20process%20of%20enlightenment.%20Even%20in%20modern%20India%2C%20everyone%20expected%20students%20to%20follow%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20footsteps.%20An%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20child%20becoming%20an%20engineer%2C%20a%20professor%E2%80%99s%20child%20becoming%20a%20professor%2C%20and%20a%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20child%20becoming%20a%20doctor%20was%20still%20the%20norm.%20There%20were%20no%20laurels%20for%20unsettling%20the%20apple%20cart%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModern%20India%20witnessed%20attempts%20from%20progressive%20sections%20to%20educate%20people%20from%20all%20quarters%20of%20society%20%E2%80%93%20people%20from%20lower-castes%2C%20workers%2C%20women%2C%20rural%20folk%20%E2%80%93%20which%20yielded%20mixed%20results.%20The%20modern%20democratic%20state%2C%20with%20a%20constitution%20that%20promised%20equal%20rights%20to%20all%2C%20aspired%20to%20usher%20in%20a%20revolution.%20Dr.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20recognised%20early%20on%20that%20political%20democracy%20hinges%20upon%20social%20democracy%20and%20that%20social%20democracy%20is%20closely%20linked%20to%20equal%20opportunities%20for%20all%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study.%20Whatever%20little%20has%20been%20achieved%20today%20is%20a%20result%20of%20this%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsix-tables-that-tell-the-story-of-academic-unfreedom-in-india%5C%22%3E%20Six%20Tables%20That%20Tell%20The%20Story%20Of%20Academic%20Unfreedom%20In%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModern%20science%20evolved%20with%20the%20strength%20of%20values%20such%20as%20falsifiability%2C%20objectivity%2C%20proof%2C%20and%2C%20finally%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20peer%20review.%20Whatever%20is%20not%20supported%20by%20proof%20is%20not%20acceptable.%20Similarly%2C%20concepts%20like%20equality%2C%20fraternity%2C%20freedom%2C%20rights%2C%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20aesthetics%2C%20and%20many%20more%20complex%20ideas%20came%20to%20define%20the%20humanities%20and%20social%20sciences%20scholarship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20university%20in%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20exactly%20are%20the%20institutions%20of%20higher%20education%20and%20how%20are%20they%20different%20from%20other%20institutions%20such%20as%20a%20home%2C%20village%2C%20city%2C%20neighbourhood%20and%20residential%20societies%3F%20Universities%20could%20very%20well%20belong%20to%20what%20the%20French%20philosopher%20Michel%20Foucault%20elaborated%20as%20heterotopia%20pr%20the%20%E2%80%98other%20places%E2%80%99.%20Universities%20are%20where%20new%20ideas%20are%20tested%20and%20that%20testing%20requires%20encouragement%20and%20a%20collaborative%20atmosphere.%20What%20one%20cannot%20discuss%20at%20home%20or%20in%20society%2C%20one%20must%20be%20able%20to%20discuss%20at%20the%20university.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstitutions%20like%20like%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%20and%20visionaries%20who%20founded%20aspirational%20universities%20such%20as%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20(Visva%20Bharati)%2C%20Jamsetji%20Tata%20(IISc)%2C%20and%20Sir%20Syed%20Ahmed%20Khan%20(Aligarh%20Muslim%20University)%20were%20attempting%20to%20create%20enlightened%20spaces.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20spirit%20of%20academic%20freedom%20and%20free%20inquiry%20has%20petered%20out%20gradually.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20other%20universities%2C%20however%2C%20had%20no%20such%20ambitions.%20Some%20of%20them%20have%20been%20wary%20of%20imbibing%20the%20harder%20part%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20university.%20Others%20were%20simply%20unaware%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20university%20was%20a%20far%20deeper%20one%20than%20they%20had%20initially%20imagined%20and%20no%20number%20of%20glittering%20edifices%20would%20be%20able%20to%20capture%20it.%20Yet%20others%20were%20there%20for%20purposes%20unrelated%20to%20enlightenment%20in%20the%20first%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20these%20led%20to%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20scepticism%20and%20fear%20among%20academics%20who%20constantly%20worried%20about%20the%20implications%20of%20their%20work%20and%20indulged%20in%20self-censorship.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20them%20have%20been%20weak%20and%20vulnerable.%20This%20nagging%20fear%20of%20retribution%20led%20to%20silence%20marking%20the%20times%2C%20what%20I%20call%20the%20%E2%80%98era%20of%20the%20silenced%20academic%E2%80%99.%20This%20situation%20is%20even%20more%20alarming%20in%20the%20private%20universities%20where%20no%20job%20security%20is%20assured.%20Interestingly%2C%20it%20was%20all%20very%20much%20in%20line%20with%20what%20a%20traditional%20Indian%20family%20taught%20its%20kids%3A%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20a%20good%20child%20and%20never%20question%20your%20elders%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20era%20of%20the%20silenced%20academic%20augmented%20the%20process%20of%20anti-enlightenment%20skilling%20in%20disciplines%20not%20limited%20to%20engineering%2C%20medicine%2C%20and%20information%20technology.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20coaching%20institutes%20and%20ed-tech%20businesses%20followed.%20All%20that%20mindless%20drilling%20took%20a%20heavy%20toll%20on%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20students%20and%20ultimately%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20a%20society%20where%20independent%20thought%20is%20penalised.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20university%20changed%20too.%20A%20university%20has%20become%20a%20place%20where%20the%20government%20in%20power%20is%20venerated%20by%20sycophants.%20The%20word%20%E2%80%98critical%E2%80%99%2C%20though%20widely%20used%20as%20in%20%E2%80%98critical%20theory%E2%80%99%2C%20aroused%20suspicion.%20The%20last%20decade%20under%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20which%20is%20opposed%20to%20criticism%20of%20any%20kind%2C%20streamlined%20the%20process%20that%20was%20already%20underway.%20A%20vicious%20government%2C%20lack%20of%20occupational%20freedoms%20and%20securities%2C%20and%20deep%20socio-cultural%20intolerance%20have%20all%20contributed%20to%20the%20frozen%20silence%20of%20the%20Indian%20academic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20way%20forward%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20must%20think%20of%20a%20system%20that%20defines%20the%20rights%2C%20tenure%2C%20duties%2C%20and%20privileges%20of%20academics%20and%20make%20its%20academic%20pillar%20as%20strong%20as%20the%20judicial%2C%20executive%2C%20and%20the%20legislative%20ones.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faaup-ui.org%2FDocuments%2FPrinciples%2FGen_Dec_Princ.pdf%5C%22%3E1915%20Declaration%20of%20Principle%3C%2Fa%3Es%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20document%20that%20proclaimed%20the%20principles%20regarding%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20tenure%20%E2%80%93%20by%20the%20American%20Association%20of%20University%20Professors%20is%20one%20such%20example.%20This%20document%20remains%20the%20%3Cem%3EMagna%20Carta%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20western%20academic%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20India%20wants%20to%20produce%20some%20excellent%20universities%20and%20aspires%20to%20become%20a%20genuine%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVishwa%20Guru%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20teacher%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%20should%20strengthen%20its%20academic%20pillar.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20academic%20bureaucracy%20should%20enable%20this%20process%20wholeheartedly%20instead%20of%20getting%20insecure%20about%20academics%20critiquing%20the%20system.%20They%20should%20realize%20that%20critical%20thought%20is%20a%20product%20of%20great%20value%20and%20nothing%20else%20can%20compensate%20for%20it.%20Constant%20governmental%20intervention%20in%20the%20everyday%20life%20of%20universities%20must%20stop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20ensuring%20job%20security%20and%20regular%2C%20decent%20payment%20for%20academics%20across%20different%20kinds%20of%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20public%2C%20private%20and%20institutions%20where%20the%20two%20work%20in%20partnership%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20necessary%20and%20unavoidable%20first%20step.%20Legal%20protection%20must%20be%20ensured%20to%20make%20this%20work.%20Ad%20hoc%20exploitation%20of%20teachers%20and%20temporary%20appointments%20must%20give%20way%20to%20regularised%20positions.%20Academic%20appointments%20must%20be%20made%20fair%20and%20academic%20institutions%20should%20be%20better%20regulated%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20a%20fair%20and%20open%20internal%20system%20is%20always%20maintained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20high%20time%20India%20turns%20an%20ancient%2C%20regimented%20nightmare%20into%20an%20inclusive%2C%20rational%2C%20and%20democratic%20dream.%20The%20era%20of%20the%20silenced%20academic%20must%20end%2C%20and%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20the%20academics%20to%20fearlessly%20express%20their%20views.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EVinod%20Kottayil%20Kalidasan%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20his%20current%20academic%20research%20is%20on%20universities%20and%20the%20education%20system%20in%20modern%20India.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710320443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21130942%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-21-at-1.06.53-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-era-of-the-silenced-academic-must-end%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20vicious%20government%2C%20lack%20of%20occupational%20f