bal%20performance%20during%20Samvaad%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStrengthening%20the%20footprints%20of%20tribal%20identity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2013%20elements%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20which%20have%20emerged%20over%20the%20years%2C%20creating%20a%20permanent%20space%20for%20dialogue%20and%20conversations%20that%20are%20poised%20to%20tackle%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20This%20annual%20conclave%20not%20only%20celebrates%20tribal%20art%20and%20culture%20but%20also%20fosters%20dialogue%20to%20drive%20change%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeld%20from%2015%20to%2019%20November%20each%20year%2C%20Samvaad%20honours%20the%20legacy%20of%20Birsa%20Munda%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tribal%20independence%20activist%20and%20leader%20from%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Munda%20tribe.%20In%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20themed%20%E2%80%98Walk%20with%20Me%E2%80%99%2C%20Samvaad%20reflected%20on%20a%20decade%20of%20impactful%20dialogues%2C%20recognising%20the%20journey%20of%20ideas%20and%20changemakers%20shaping%20the%20present%20and%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20different%20elements%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eincluding%20f%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eo%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161926%2Fandhra-pradesh-araku-coffee-gold-paris-news%2F%5C%22%3Eod%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20music%2C%20artisans%2C%20cultural%20markers%2C%20and%20others%2C%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20intangible%20potential%20through%20this%20tribal%20cultural%20conclave.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20platform%20of%20expression%20but%20also%20a%20forum%20for%20meaningful%20dialogues%20that%20add%20perspectives%20to%20the%20different%20aspects%20of%20life%20and%20one%E2%80%99s%20journey%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sourav%20Roy%2C%20CEO%20of%20TSF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThroughout%20the%20year%2C%20we%20engage%20with%20the%20tribes%20through%20our%20initiatives%20to%20converge%20on%20dialogues%20that%20set%20the%20tone%20for%20Samvaad%20each%20year.%20Many%20new%20ideas%20and%20innovations%20emerge%20from%20these%20conversations%2C%20moderated%20by%20experts%20from%20respective%20fields%20and%20changemakers%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20Celebration%20of%20culture%20also%20forms%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20which%20not%20only%20generates%20livelihood%20for%20tribal%20artisans%20but%20also%20allows%20people%20to%20appreciate%20their%20unique%20traditions%2C%20passed%20down%20through%20generations%2C%20rich%20in%20wisdom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESamvaad%E2%80%99s%20varied%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%20of%20Samvaad%20is%20reflected%20in%20its%20diverse%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20includes%20promoting%20tribal%20healers%2C%20artisans%2C%20cuisines%2C%20languages%2C%20sports%20and%20heritage%20conservation%2C%20%3Cem%3EAkhra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESamudaay%20ke%20Saath%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%2C%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%2C%20and%20Samvaad%20Action%20Research%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samvaad%20Fellowship%20aims%20to%20guide%20and%20nurture%20individuals%20committed%20to%20preserving%20tribal%20culture%20and%20heritage%20through%20community-based%20action.%20After%20a%20round%20of%20assessments%2C%20the%20fellows%20receive%20one-year%20grants%20and%20mentorships%20from%20academicians%20and%20experts.%20These%20fellowships%20have%20led%20to%20tangible%20outcomes%20like%20tribal%20dictionaries%2C%20song%20recordings%2C%20story%20books%20for%20children%2C%20collectives%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20contesting%20elections%20to%20making%20documentaries%20on%20tribal%20issues%2C%20many%20people%20have%20emerged%20as%20leaders%20and%20changemakers.%20Some%20have%20even%20failed.%20Irrespective%20of%20your%20failure%20or%20success%2C%20you%20have%20made%20friends%20who%20will%20always%20support%20you.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20Samvaad%20aims%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jiren%20Xavier%20Topno%2C%20Head%20of%20Tribal%20Identity%20at%20TSF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201915px)%20100vw%2C%201915px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221915%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Participants%20at%20the%20Akhra%20event%20in%20Samvaad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480.jpg%201915w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fakhra3_11zon-1710165480-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344565%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParticipants%20at%20the%20Akhra%20event%20in%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamvaad%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3E10tak%20at%20Akhra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20another%20way%20in%20which%20the%20conclave%20served%20as%20a%20platform%20where%20individuals%20from%20diverse%20tribal%20groups%20came%20together%20to%20share%20their%20journey%20of%20change%2C%20challenges%2C%20and%20possible%20solutions.%20As%20Samvaad%20stepped%20into%20its%20tenth%20year%2C%20over%20500%20people%20gathered%20to%20share%20their%20inspiring%20stories%20at%20the%20open-air%20Amphitheatre%20at%20the%20Tribal%20Cultural%20Centre%20(TCC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20Pawar%2C%20instigated%20by%20the%20rising%20farmer%20suicides%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20fought%20for%20his%20rights%20and%20now%20runs%20constitution%20schools%20to%20educate%20his%20community%20about%20their%20rights%3B%20Manasi%20from%20Odisha%20helped%20bring%20back%20thousands%20of%20migrant%20labourers%20amid%20the%20pandemic%20by%20being%20a%20citizen%20journalist%3B%20and%20Garima%20Siddhar%20is%20a%20lawyer%20providing%20justice%20to%20tribal%20communities.%20These%20changemakers%20are%20now%20a%20part%20of%20the%20tribal%20leadership%20programme%20alumni%2C%20which%20is%20over%20400-%20members%20strong%2C%20who%20have%20stayed%20connected%20to%20share%20their%20narratives%20of%20change%20to%20inspire%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cultural%20lens%2C%20Samvaad%20organises%20a%20grand%20inaugural%20show%20every%20year%20at%20Gopal%20Maidan.%20This%20year%2C%20251%20%3Cem%3Enagadas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edhols%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20musical%20instruments%20reverberated%20in%20homage%20to%20Birsa%20Munda.%20The%20tribals%20adorning%20bright%20yellow%20vests%20with%20white%20%3Cem%3Edhotis%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20played%20various%20goosebump-inducing%20songs%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebonga%20taal%2C%20baika%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esantal%20taal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDancers%20and%20singers%20participated%20in%20cultural%20performances%20as%20people%20gorged%20on%20tribal%20delicacies%2C%20shopped%20for%20vibrant%20artefacts%20(handcrafted%20by%20the%20same%20artisans%20who%20are%20selling%20them)%2C%20and%20danced%20to%20the%20tribal%20beats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20and%20I%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20Samvaad%20since%20the%20beginning.%20I%20love%20the%20energy%20here.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20highlight%20is%20selling%20our%20Oraon%20paintings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20a%20painter%20from%20Chhattisgarh.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20few%20people%20knew%20about%20our%20paintings%20before%2C%20but%20now%20it%20is%20more%20popular.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20only%20handicrafts%20stalls%2C%20but%20Samvaad%20has%20grown%20so%20much%20with%20%3Cem%3EAkhara%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20fellowship%2C%20tribal%20healers%2C%20Tribal%20Leadership%20Programme%20and%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Choisa%20Hakong%20from%20the%20Chakesang%20tribe%20(Nagaland)%20was%20at%20the%20conclave%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20%E2%80%9CSamvaad%20is%20connecting%20tribals%20as%20one%20in%20spirit%20and%20culture.%20I%20am%20so%20happy%20to%20attend%20and%20showcase%20our%20products%20made%20from%20teak%20and%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20five%20days%2C%20Pritesh%2C%20Sumanti%2C%20and%20Choisa%2C%20along%20with%20people%20from%20110%20other%20tribes%2C%20displayed%20their%20cuisine%2C%20artwork%2C%20and%20healing%20practices.%20Besides%20the%20stalls%2C%20140%20home%20chefs%20from%2037%20tribes%20offered%20home%20delivery%20via%20the%20Zomato%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20these%20artisans%20goes%20beyond%20selling%20their%20products.%20They%20also%20refine%20their%20skills%20through%20workshops%20and%20sessions%20led%20by%20handicraft%20experts%2C%20engage%20in%20healing%20practices%2C%20and%20showcase%20their%20culinary%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tribal%20food%20at%20display%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-2048x1152.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPritesh_Kumar_Khalko_para_1._11zon-1710165476-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344564%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETribal%20food%20displayed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20stalls%20at%20Samvaad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20tangible%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20of%20Samvaad%2C%20the%20initiative%20has%20seen%20a%20visible%20impact%2C%20bringing%20together%20over%2040%2C000%20people%20from%20India%20and%2017%20other%20countries.%20The%20beauty%20of%20this%20conclave%20is%20that%20it%20extends%20beyond%20the%20five%20days%3B%20the%20dialogue%20and%20actions%20continue%20throughout%20the%20year.%20This%20meticulous%20approach%20has%20led%20to%20outcomes%20that%20once%20seemed%20far-fetched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%E2%80%98Rhythms%20of%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20