0source%3A%20Seema%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20kids%E2%80%99%20lives%20in%20real-time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20of%20time%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20dreams%20of%20Nayi%20Disha.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20handful%20of%20kids%20being%20taught%20English%20in%20a%20small%20room%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20now%20scaled%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335548%2Fthis-hero-turned-mud-walls-into-blackboards-streets-into-schools-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20100%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20spread%20across%20eight%20rooms%20learning%20a%20variety%20of%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20mathematics%2C%20environmental%20science%2C%20art%2C%20computers%20and%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20astounding%20than%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20participation%20has%20been%20the%20support%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20notes%20Seema.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20begun%20to%20see%20an%20improvement%20in%20their%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20realisation%20deepened%20during%20the%20lockdown%20that%20ensued%20amid%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20online%20classes%2C%20it%20so%20happened%20that%20parents%20were%20at%20home%20while%20the%20kids%20were%20learning.%20We%20would%20send%20them%20activities%20and%20worksheets%20to%20solve.%20The%20parents%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearning%20a%20lot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20bargain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lockdown%2C%20the%20entire%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20knew%20the%20days%20of