known%20as%20%3Cem%3Echampi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341024%2Fshark-tank-india-radhika-gupta-advice-on-motherhood-career-parenting-mom-guilt-work-life-balance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emother%20or%20%3Cem%3Edaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E(grandmother).%20The%20oil%2C%20made%20by%20her%20grandmother%2C%20would%20be%20applied%20lovingly%20on%20her%20hair%2C%20with%20stories%20galore.%20The%20secret%20recipe%20helped%20her%20hair%20grow%20%E2%80%98long%20and%20strong%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20went%20to%20college%2C%20and%20later%20work%2C%20this%20weekly%20ritual%20ceased%20to%20be%2C%20as%20other%20priorities%20cropped%20up.%20She%20had%20almost%20forgotten%20about%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20hair%20oil%2C%20which%20protected%20and%20nourished%20her%20hair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20contracted%20COVID-19%2C%20the%20Gurugram%20resident%20experienced%20a%20massive%20hair%20fall%2C%20as%20did%20her%20mother-in-law%20Rajni%20(67).%20During%20this%20time%2C%20in%202020%2C%20the%2040-year-old%20remembered%20her%20daadi%E2%80%99s%20oil%20and%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20She%20got%20the%20family%20recipe%20from%20her%20mother%20and%20asked%20her%20mother-in-law%20if%20she%20could%20make%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20of%20them%20tried%20it%2C%20and%20lo%20and%20behold%2C%20within%20three%20months%2C%20the%20two%20women%20saw%20visible%20changes.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20she%20heard%20women%20at%20her%20apartment%20complex%20discuss%20hair%20fall%20problems.%20As%20they%20discussed%20possible%20solutions%2C%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20oil%20emerged%20as%20a%20clear%20winner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mother-in-law%2C%20daughter-in-law%20duo%20then%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20help%20women%20at%20their%20apartment%20regain%20their%20long%20locks%20again.%20Starting%20with%20a%20small%20batch%20of%20one%20litre%2C%20the%20response%20pushed%20them%20to%20consider%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20Dua%20launched%20%E2%80%98Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20sells%20hair%20oil%20for%20%E2%80%98hair%20fall%20control%E2%80%99%2C%20shampoo%2C%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub.%20Launched%20on%20a%20Whatsapp%20group%2C%20the%20oil%20has%20found%20its%20way%20to%20over%2067%2C000%20homes%2C%20selling%20over%20one%20lakh%20bottles%20and%20earning%20a%20monthly%20income%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakhs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20this%20story%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20run%20by%20a%20mother%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20helping%20them%20gain%20financial%20freedom%20and%20giving%20wings%20to%20their%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20an%20age%20old%20problem%20faced%20by%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi%20and%20Rajni%20make%20the%20hair%20oil%20using%2013%20ingredients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi1-min-1709646600-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%