C%20packaging%2C%20customer%20support%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20website%20all%20by%20themselves.%20After%20the%20success%20of%20their%20oil%2C%20they%20introduced%20a%20shampoo%20using%20Rajni%E2%80%99s%20recipe%2C%20a%20conditioner%2C%20scalp%20scrub%20and%20comb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20they%20have%20over%208%2C000%20orders%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20secret%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20938px)%20100vw%2C%20938px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nidhi's%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312.jpeg%20938w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-176x300.jpeg%20176w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-500x853.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-768x1310.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-900x1536.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fnidhi2-1709647312-150x256.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandma%20Secret%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20Panchkula%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20oil%20sell%20out%20and%20attract%20repeat%20customers%3F%20Nidhi%20states%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98100%20percent%20natural%20and%20homemade%E2%80%99.%20The%20oil%20is%20made%20using%20a%20secret%20mix%20of%2013%20herbs%20with%20coconut%20oil%20as%20the%20base.%20Without%20revealing%20the%20secret%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20what%20Nidhi%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20the%20oil%20in%20an%20iron%20kadhai%2C%20add%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20add%20each%20of%20the%20ingredients%20one%20by%20one.%20We%20cook%20it%20for%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20after%20which%20we%20rest%20it%20for%208-10%20hours.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20we%20strain%20it%20using%20a%20cotton%20cloth%20and%20reheat%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20then%20cooled%2C%20strained%20and%20packed%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Nidhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingredients%20include%20curry%20leaf%20and%20aloe%20vera%20gel%20among%20others.%20They%20make%20about%20100%20litres%20of%20oil%20in%20two%20days%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamaljeet%20Arya%2C%20one%20of%20their%20customers%2C%20says%20that%20the%20hair%20oil%20and%20shampoo%20have%20had%20a%20tremendous%20impact%20for%20her.%20She%20faced%20hairfall%20issues%20as%20she%20is%20peri-menopausal%20and%20has%20thyroid%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20tried%20many%20different%20products%20over%20the%20years%20but%20nothing%20really%20worked.%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Nidhi%E2%80%99s%20Grandmaa%20Secret%20through%20a%20friend%20and%20have%20been%20using%20it%20for%20five%20months%20now.%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20noticeable%20difference%20in%20my%20hair%2C%20my%20hair%20fall%20has%20greatly%20reduced.%20My%20son%2C%20too%2C%20uses%20it%20and%20has%20seen%20good%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kamaljeet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20six%20months%2C%20the%20duo%20just%20worked%20on%20fulfilling%20orders.%20There%20would%20be%20oil%20simmering%20on%20the%20gas%20morning%2C%20afternoon%20and%20evening%3B%20with%20its%20shelf%20life%20of%20three%20years.%20As%20orders%20crossed%20almost%20300%20per%20day%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20it%20could%20no%20longer%20be%20managed%20from%20home.%3C%2Fp%3